    short_description:
      'Join LastPass as a Software Development Engineer in Test (SDET) and contribute to building top-quality web applications. Collaborate with a diverse team of professionals and tackle exciting challenges like test plan creation and CI/CD verification loops. Requirements include professional software product experience, strong Java skills, and familiarity with test automation tools like Selenium. Apply now to be part of a market-leading, inclusive environment that values your growth and unique perspective.',
