      'Strategic Planning, Decision-Making, Business Document Creation, Budget Management, Partnership Oversight, Entrepreneurial Spirit, Adaptability, Mentoring, Team Management, Business Finance, Continuous Improvement, Crypto Industry Knowledge, Collaboration, Partnership Management',
    description:
      "The VP of Business Development at Kadena plays a pivotal role in driving the growth of the ecosystem through strategic planning and decision-making. You will collaborate closely with Business Development and Strategy departments to stay informed about current and future developments within Kadena, translating this knowledge into actionable business and strategic roadmaps. As the ecosystem expands, you will need to adapt to new initiatives, manage and scale companies, and identify strategic opportunities that contribute to ecosystem growth. Your entrepreneurial spirit and ability to embrace challenges in a fast-paced industry will be crucial.\n\nIn this role, you will directly engage with Kadena's leadership to refine business strategies, manage the Business Development budget, oversee the grants program, and establish key partnerships. Leading and mentoring the Business Development team to exceed targets, fostering relationships, prospecting new opportunities, and addressing operational needs within Kadena and related companies will be part of your responsibilities. Collaboration with various departments, maintaining progress documentation, and supporting ecosystem companies will also be key aspects of your role.\n\nTo excel as the VP of Business Development, you should have over 5 years of experience in financial or business development, complex operations, and mentoring individuals. Proficiency in creating high-quality business documents, familiarity with cryptocurrency, and a degree in Business/Finance are preferred. Kadena requires all employees to be fully vaccinated against COVID-19. The annual salary for this role ranges from $170,000 to $270,000, with additional benefits such as medical, vision, and dental insurance, flexible savings accounts, unlimited PTO, and more.\n\nIf you are passionate about driving growth, shaping strategies, and contributing to the success of a dynamic ecosystem, apply now to join Kadena, the industry's leading scalable blockchain platform.",
