    description:
      'Realiste AI is seeking a Financial Management Specialist to join our dynamic team in Dubai. As a Financial Management Specialist at Realiste AI, you will be responsible for obtaining financial loans from banks and funds to support real estate development projects, collaborating with developers to expedite timelines, and reducing overdue accounts receivable. The ideal candidate will have work experience in B2B credit brokerage, development management, or investment attraction in the UAE, with a strong financial background and fluency in Russian and English. You will enjoy a competitive compensation package, opportunities for career growth based on performance, and the chance to acquire stock options after 6 months of successful employment. If you are ready to contribute to our mission of revolutionizing real estate investments, we invite you to apply for this exciting opportunity at Realiste AI.',
