    job_requirements:
      '• At least 2-3 years of experience in sales, account management, or customer success, preferably in a B2B or HR Tech environment.\n   - Refinement: The ideal candidate should have a proven track record in engaging with customers at various levels, building trust, and fostering long-term relationships. Experience in B2B or HR Tech industries is a plus.\n   \n• Strong communication skills to effectively build rapport with clients and team members.\n   - Refinement: Excellent verbal and written communication skills are essential to ensure clear and effective interactions with customers and internal teams.\n   \n• Ability to thrive in a fast-paced environment, managing multiple projects simultaneously while prioritizing tasks efficiently.\n   - Refinement: The candidate should demonstrate adaptability, resilience, and strong organizational skills to succeed in a dynamic work setting with shifting priorities.\n   \n• Comfortable with ambiguity and risk, actively seeking opportunities for self-improvement and innovation in work processes.\n   - Refinement: The role requires a proactive and self-starting individual who is open to taking risks, embracing uncertainty, and continuously seeking ways to enhance their work methods.\n   \n• Experience using customer engagement tools like Vitally, Hubspot, Intercom, and Slack channels to communicate with customers and track data.\n   - Refinement: Proficiency in utilizing various customer management platforms and tools to enhance customer interactions, monitor feedback, and identify growth opportunities is highly desirable.\n   \n• Collaborative mindset with the ability to work effectively with team members from diverse cultural backgrounds and time zones.\n   - Refinement: The candidate should be adept at collaborating with colleagues across different regions and time zones, fostering a culture of teamwork, inclusivity, and mutual support.',
